reviewText: My son loves this show. Malays it over and over.
My sister got this for the kids at her job. She said they enjoyed the Rugrats and watched all the series without noise.

One of my favorite cartoons as a kid. I don't care how old I get - I still want to watch Rugrats! This is a Halloween special with Chuckie being dressed up as a werewolf/werewuff. Angelica being bad and the gang all there. Also some extra episodes from the series. Super cute.
Fast shipping grand kids love it thank you
I was expecting all the rugrats Halloween episodes. This does have 5 episodes but only 1 of them is an actual Halloween episode
Listing said New, but the package wasn't wrapped like a new movie, cover was torn and case looked like it had been chewed on.
